_sText:
I wanted to do something different so I added AK, colt, AWP, and HE in the same map. The lower level is HE, the middle (biggest) level is AWP and the top level is AK and colt. This map is made for 16 players and has 5 different spawn points for each team.

This map is bot ready.

**DO NOT EDIT OR CHANGE ANY PARTS OF THIS MAP WITHOUT MY PERMISSION

** I don't mind people using this map on their server just as long as they give me the IP so that I may play as well =)

-Skeeter
